# Dynamic Categories - Records & Relations System

Complete implementation guide for adding advanced record management with bidirectional relationships to your Dynamic Categories application.

## 📋 Table of Contents

1. [Overview](#overview)
2. [Features](#features)
3. [Architecture](#architecture)
