## 📊 Example Use Cases

### Medical Records System

```javascript
// Record: Medication
{
  title: "PAND-2024-001",
  customFields: [
    { label: "Manufacturer", value: "QQQ3 Pharma" },
    { label: "Batch Number", value: "B12345" },
    { label: "Expiry Date", value: "2025-12-31" },
    { label: "Dosage", value: "500mg" },
    { label: "Storage Temp", value: "15-25°C" }
  ]
}

// Relations
manufactured_by → QQQ3 Pharma (Supplier)
stored_in → Storage Unit A-23
```

### Inventory Management

```javascript
// Record: Product
{
  title: "Laptop-XYZ-123",
  customFields: [
    { label: "SKU", value: "LAP-XYZ-123" },
    { label: "Quantity", value: "50" },
    { label: "Unit Price", value: "$999.99" },
    { label: "Reorder Level", value: "10" }
  ]
}

// Relations
supplied_by → Supplier ABC
stored_in → Warehouse B
related_to → Laptop-XYZ-124 (similar model)
```

### Project Management

```javascript
// Record: Task
{
  title: "Implement Authentication",
  customFields: [
    { label: "Assignee", value: "John Doe" },
    { label: "Priority", value: "High" },
    { label: "Due Date", value: "2024-12-31" },
    { label: "Estimated Hours", value: "8" }
  ]
}

// Relations
depends_on → Setup Firebase Project
parent_of → Create Login Form
parent_of → Add Password Reset
```

